                    <h1 class="text-left" id="L4_Title" data-title="Lesson 4: Water in Brewing" style="font-family:'fira-sans-2';color:black">Water in Brewing</h1>
                    <p class="text-left" style="font-size:larger;color:black">
                        <b>
                            In this lesson we'll talk about the importance of water in brewing.
                        </b>
                        <br />
                        <span><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> Estimated Lesson Time: 8 min.</span>
                        <br />
